MySQL Queries:
1) In order to show the databases available in mysql
   show databases;
   
2) In order to create a database in mysql
   create database dbname;
   
3) In order to delete a database in mysql
   drop database dbname;

4) For selecting a database among multiple databases
   use dbname;

5) Inorder to see the tables inside the database 
   show tables;
   
6) For creating a table in MySQL
   create table employee(eid int, ename varchar(15), address varchar(20));
   
7) Describe table structure
   desc employee;
 
8) Insert data into the table
   insert into employee values (1,'Giridhar','Banglore');
   
9) Inorder to see the records inside a table
   select * from employee;
   
10) I know the table columns but i dont know the column order
    insert into employee (address, eid, ename) values ('Banglore',2,'Raju');
	
11) Insert data into a specific columns
    insert into employee (address,ename) values('Bangalore','Hari');
	
12) How to update a record in a table
    update employee set eid=3 where ename='Hari';